title: I did not get the 10th anniversary icon

replies.body: Gifts are not done yet per our [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-).  Give it some more time for all of this to wrap up!  You'll get your goods.  :D

I too have yet to receive my icon and Mystery Gift (since I already have Riot Kayle) :( 

Are they still rolling out? I've played a bagillion Aram games in the last couple of months or even just since I started League like... 5 years ago, but I played maybe 1 SR game on the 18th of September by coincidence. Otherwise my last Ranked/SR was in May. 

Does aram count as "1 game"?
